        {"source": "S3", "quote": "we propose a novel method, LLM-Planner, that harnesses the power of large language models to do few-shot planning for embodied agents."},
        {"source": "S4", "quote": "We further propose a simple but effective way to enhance LLMs with physical grounding to generate and update plans that are grounded in the current environment."}
      ],
      "reason": "The abstract mentions a method for few-shot planning and enhancing LLMs with physical grounding, but it does not specify how prompts are constructed, structured, or constrained, leaving the prompt-engineering operation unclear."
