      "reason": "The method uses LLMs for planning and grounding, but it is not stated whether it requires training of model weights or can be applied purely through prompting; thus it is unclear if it is practitioner-usable without training."
    },
    {
      "id": "E1_NO_ACTIONABLE_TECHNIQUE",
