      "evidence": [
        {"source": "S1", "quote": "using large language models (LLMs) as a planner for embodied agents that can follow natural language instructions to complete complex tasks in a visually-perceived environment."},
        {"source": "S3", "quote": "propose a novel method, LLM-Planner, that harnesses the power of large language models to do few-shot planning for embodied agents."}
      ],
      "reason": "The article reports a domain application (embodied agents) of an LLM but does not describe the prompt method in actionable detail, as the prompt technique is not clearly specified."
